<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Coffeespots</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Welcome to CoffeeSpots</h1>
<a href="/">home</a>
<% if user_signed_in? %>	
	<%= current_user.email %>
	<%= link_to "log out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
<% else %>
	<p>welcome, please sign in or sign up</p>
	<%= link_to "sign in", new_user_session_path %>
	<%= link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path %>
<% end %>	
<p>CoffeeSpots is a way to guage the consistency of a cup of coffee in this city. Let us know how good that brew was!</p>
<p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
<p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
<%= yield %>

</body>
</html>
